Installation:
	git clone git://github.com/samharad/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/dotfiles/bashrc ~/.bashrc
	ln -s ~/dotfiles/bash_profile ~/.bash_profile
	ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vim ~/.vim
	ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/dotfiles/.ssh ~/.ssh

To install a plugin initially:
	cd .vim
	git submodule add <github link> bundle/<plugin name>

To get plugins:
	cd .vim/bundles
	git submodule init
	git submodule upfate
	

